OL,3,CDaughter speaks of 'void' in letter a
OL,4,Cdecade on from father's unsolved murder
OL,6,FThe 12-year-old daughter of a man who
OL,7,Fwas stabbed and killed while walking
OL,8,Fhome in Hereford on Father's Day 10
OL,9,Fyears ago, has written a heartfelt
OL,10,Fletter sharing the "void" that's
OL,11,Falways there in her life.
OL,13,FChristian Bagley had been to see his
OL,14,F19-month-old daughter at his ex-
OL,15,Fpartner's house on Sunday, 21 June,
OL,16,F2015.
