OL,3,CDaughter speaks of 'void' in letter a
OL,4,Cdecade on from father's unsolved murder
OL,6,FAs the 30-year-old walked home towards
OL,7,FHunderton Bridge, along Villa Street
OL,8,Fadjacent to the River Wye and
OL,9,Funderneath the Great Western Way
OL,10,Ffootpath, known locally as 'The
OL,11,FLines', Christian was stabbed with
OL,12,Fwhat's believed to be a kitchen knife.
OL,14,FAfter being attacked near the concrete
OL,15,Fsteps linking the street to 'The
OL,16,FLines', Christian staggered to Charles
OL,17,FWitts Avenue.
