OL,6,FThe weapon remained embedded in his
OL,7,Fleft arm, but the handle that snapped
OL,8,Foff during the attack has never been
OL,9,Ffound.
OL,11,FA 999 call was made to the ambulance
OL,12,Fservice shortly after Christian was
OL,13,Fstabbed. The caller, asking for help
OL,14,Fexplains; "He's lost a lot of blood."
OL,16,FEmergency services were called to the
OL,17,Fscene, but were unable to save him and
OL,18,Fhe died from his injuries.
