OL,3,CDaughter speaks of 'void' in letter a
OL,4,Cdecade on from father's unsolved murder
OL,6,FAlmost 10 years on, it's still not
OL,7,Fknown who stabbed him and West Mercia
OL,8,FPolice continue to investigate.
OL,10,FNo-one has ever been charged with
OL,11,FChristian's murder. Although several
OL,12,Fsuspects were arrested around the
OL,13,Ftime, they were later released without
OL,14,Fcharge and the case remains unsolved.
OL,16,FChristian Bagley's daughter was just
OL,17,F19-months-old when her father died on
OL,18,FFather's Day. A decade on from his
OL,19,Fdeath, she's shared a heartfelt
OL,20,Fmessage in the hope of one day getting
OL,21,Fanswers.
