OL,3,CDaughter speaks of 'void' in letter a
OL,4,Cdecade on from father's unsolved murder
OL,6,FHer letter reads: "Somebody taking my
OL,7,Fdad away from me when I was little is
OL,8,Fsomething that can never be replaced.
OL,9,FI have no memories of my dad or his
OL,10,Fpresence in my life - only what other
OL,11,Fpeople have told me.
OL,13,F"I was never given the chance to get
OL,14,Fto know him or for him to watch me
OL,15,Fgrow up. I'll never be able to spend
OL,16,FFather's Day, Christmas Day or a
OL,17,Fbirthday with my dad.
OL,19,F"There's an emptiness that should not
OL,20,Fbe inside me because somebody murdered
OL,21,Fmy dad.
OL,26,@nD@SOUuD@AOU{D@AOU
