OL,3,CDaughter speaks of 'void' in letter a
OL,4,Cdecade on from father's unsolved murder
OL,6,F"That void within myself will always
OL,7,Fbe there.
OL,9,F"Everything he did that day ` 21.06.15
OL,10,F` was a 'last time' experience.
OL,12,F"They still haven't found who killed
OL,13,Fmy dad or any answers to why somebody
OL,14,Fcruelly took him away. I love you dad."
OL,16,FPaying tribute to her son on the tenth
OL,17,Fanniversary of his murder, Christian's
OL,18,Fmother, Janette, known as 'Jan'
OL,19,FBagley, described him as the "kindest
OL,20,Fperson you would ever meet."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@AOUtD@AOUvD@gO]
