OL,3,CDaughter speaks of 'void' in letter a
OL,4,Cdecade on from father's unsolved murder
OL,6,FShe said: "If I was across the water,
OL,7,Fhe'd have walked across it just to
OL,8,Fhelp us.
OL,10,F"Christian was the 'clasp' to the
OL,11,F'link'. When they took the clasp, they
OL,12,Fbroke it, whoever done it, they broke
OL,13,Fit, and the link fell one by one. They
OL,14,Ftook it away, took the family away.
OL,16,F"He loved his daughter; his daughter
OL,17,Fwas his life. When his daughter was
OL,18,Fborn, he was the most elated person
OL,19,Fyou'll ever know.
OL,26,@nD@KOUrD@AOUxD@AOU
