OL,3,CDaughter speaks of 'void' in letter a
OL,4,Cdecade on from father's unsolved murder
OL,6,F"All I want to know is why? Why have
OL,7,Fyou done this to my boy? ` He's
OL,8,Fstabbed for no reason whatsoever. He
OL,9,Fdidn't deserve it, he's walking along,
OL,10,Fgoing home after seeing his baby
OL,11,Fdaughter on Father's Day.
OL,13,F"Please, somebody somewhere knows
OL,14,Fsomething, and I want to know why?
OL,15,FJust why? Tell me why you did this to
OL,16,Fmy boy."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
