OL,3,CDaughter speaks of 'void' in letter a
OL,4,Cdecade on from father's unsolved murder
OL,6,FA decade on and with the case still
OL,7,Funsolved, West Mercia Police continues
OL,8,Fwith its investigation and is using
OL,9,Fthe milestone to appeal to the public
OL,10,Ffor their help.
OL,12,FDetective Chief Inspector Gareth
OL,13,FLougher, of West Mercia Police's Major
OL,14,FInvestigation Unit, said: "While we
OL,15,Fhave continued to investigate this
OL,16,Fcase, a decade on it seems timelier
OL,17,Fthan ever to appeal again to the
OL,18,Fpublic to help us get justice for
OL,19,FChristian's daughter, mother and all
OL,20,Fhis family and friends.
OL,26,@vD@[OU
