OL,3,CDaughter speaks of 'void' in letter a
OL,4,Cdecade on from father's unsolved murder
OL,6,F"We hope this heartfelt message from a
OL,7,Fdaughter who has grown up never
OL,8,Fknowing her father will prick the
OL,9,Fconscience of someone carrying a
OL,10,Fburden of knowledge about his murder
OL,11,Fto step forward and help us bring
OL,12,Fthose responsible before the courts.
OL,14,F"After ten years, loyalties and
OL,15,Fallegiances may have changed, and we
OL,16,Fhope anyone who knows something will
OL,17,Fdo the right thing and speak to us."
